	<li id="comment-83440">
		<img alt='' src='http://i2.wp.com/graph.facebook.com/800405077/picture?q=type%3Dlarge%26_md5%3D7710b3f5fa7a467244beac3d2b47b0b1&#038;resize=44%2C44' class='avatar avatar-44' height='44' width='44' />		<p>
			<p>The other issue nobody talks about with HFT is the almost complete lack of system security. When every microsecond counts adding code to check for malicious and malformed messages is a luxury few can afford. The will come a time when somebody figures out how to crash or manipulate the opposing traders systems with a malformed data packet and then things will get really interesting.</p>
<p><strong>From MC&gt; right on ! </strong></p>
