<div class="pd-rating" id="pd_rating_holder_1431624_comm_83430"></div>		</p>
		<p>
			<cite>
			Comment by <a href='https://www.facebook.com/sgalbrai' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Simon Galbraith</a> - 
			<a href="http://blogmaverick.com/2014/04/03/the-idiots-guide-to-high-frequency-trading/#comment-83430">
