<div class="pd-rating" id="pd_rating_holder_1431624_comm_83356"></div>		</p>
		<p>
			<cite>
			Comment by <a href='https://www.facebook.com/greg.kruzick.7' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Greg Kruzick</a> - 
			<a href="http://blogmaverick.com/2014/04/03/the-idiots-guide-to-high-frequency-trading/#comment-83356">
				<time datetime="2014-04-03T20:49:59+00:00">
